      capacitance="10uF" 
      footprint="0805" 
      pcbX="5mm"

      name="R1" 
      resistance="10k" 
      footprint="0402" 
      pcbX="5mm" 
      pcbY="0mm"

      name="R2" 
      resistance="10k" 
      footprint="0402" 
      pcbX="5mm" 
      pcbY="5mm"

      name="LED1" 
      footprint="0805" 
      pcbX="-5mm"
